Interface FireStationNotificationImplI

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FireStationNotificationCI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FireStationFacade, FireStationNotificationConnector, FireStationNotificationInboundPort, FireStationNotificationOutboundPort

    public interface FireStationNotificationImplI
    The interface FireStationNotificationImplI defines the notifications that must be implemented to be called by a fire station.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant      true
